  "datePublished": "2026-03-08",
  "description": "Qwen is a family of open-weight large language models developed by Alibaba Cloud, released under the Apache 2.0 license.\nThe family has progressed through several generations: Qwen (2023), Qwen2 (mid-2024), Qwen2.5 (September 2024), Qwen3 (April 2025), and Qwen3.5 (early 2026).\nQwen2.5 is available in dense models at 0.5B, 1.5B, 3B, 7B, 14B, 32B, and 72B parameters. It was trained on 18 trillion tokens and is known for strong coding and math performance. Specialized variants exist for code (Qwen2.5-Coder) and math (Qwen2.5-Math).\n",
  "name": "Qwen",
